      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A 25-year-old male who had unprotected sexual intercourse 3 weeks ago is anxious about the possibility of HIV infection. He has no symptoms. He seeks advice on which test would be most sensitive to detect HIV at this stage.</span></span></p>",
