          "id": 19259,
          "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Polymerase Chain Reaction (PCR)</span></span></span></span></p>"
