      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A 32-year-old pregnant woman, who is HIV positive, is discussing her delivery plan. She wants to understand the best approach to minimize the risk of transmitting HIV to her baby. Which medication is most appropriate for preventing mother-to-child transmission of HIV?</span></span></p>",
